title.narrative: Increasing Farmer Resilience to Climate Change

description.narrative: The project is expected to impact over 500 farmers producing fresh fruit, vegetables and high value filed crops, 1,500 farmers practicing conservation agriculture, and create jobs for at least 1,000 people (mostly the youth and women).
